@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "MealPlan API" as API
database PostgreSQL
participant "Recommendation API" as Reco

User -> Frontend: Tao meal plan tu dong
Frontend -> API: POST /api/meal-plans/auto-generate
API -> Reco: lay de xuat mon an
Reco --> API: recommended foods
API -> PostgreSQL: create meal_plan + details
API --> Frontend: meal plan data
User -> Frontend: Kich hoat plan
Frontend -> API: PATCH /api/meal-plans/:id/activate
API -> PostgreSQL: update active plan
@enduml
